      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·陳風·003.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">衡門.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>衡門之下，可以棲遲。泌之洋洋，可以樂飢。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Beneath my door made of cross pieces of wood,
I can rest at my leisure;
By the wimpling stream from my fountain,
I can joy amid my hunger.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
