      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·陳風·003.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">衡門.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>豈其食魚，必河之魴。豈其取妻，必齊之姜。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Why, in eating fish,
Must we have bream from the Ho?
Why, in taking a wife,
Must we have a Keang of Tsfe?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
