      <prop type="x-translation-ref">衡門.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>豈其食魚，必河之鯉。豈其取妻，必宋之子。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Why, in eating fish,
Must we have carp from the Ho?
Why, in taking a wife,
Must we have a Tsze of Sung?</seg>
      </tuv>
